description:
Frank Siller of Tunnel to Towers calls us from their Veterans Day event at the Lincoln Memorial. Pompeo warns: We're distracted by wokeness. Wounded veteran Rick Yarosh tells us his inspiring story. Twitter throttles Buck over truthful mask tweet.
